-- ft.h3: Attributes

Boolean accepts the below attributes as well all the [common attributes ](/fifthtry/ftd/common/).

- `text`
- `line` 
- `align`
- `style`
- `format`
- `size`
- `external_font`
- `font`
- `line_height`